						is made with <i class="fa fa-heart-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> by <a href="https://colorlib.com"
							target="_blank">Colorlib</a></div>
					<!-- Link back to Colorlib can't be removed. Template is licensed under CC BY 3.0. -->
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
		<!-- End footer Area -->
	</div>
	
